    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896460/extras/a794a0bca159f5fab7b930411845d0ae.webp?t=1763928324\" width=614 height=47 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896460/extras/steamcombatgif02.JPG?t=1763928324\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >劈砍斩杀，登神封圣。《梦境天堂》是一场惊心动魄的逃离，穿越我们最可怕的噩梦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你已受选，宿命决定了你内心的恶魔终将化为凶残的噩梦。你必须为唤醒伪神赎罪。跋涉于地狱般的梦境界域，抵御噩梦的侵袭，发现<strong>接纳自己</strong>的力量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896460/extras/8abfef19ee62f8d85d0ccc6006c7a1a6.webp?t=1763928324\" width=614 height=47 /></span>￼</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896460/extras/familiarsteamgiflesscluttered.JPG?t=1763928324\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握一套深度战斗系统，将远程和近战动作与丰富多样的自定义选择相融合。探索一个隐秘的世界，这里弥漫着压抑沉郁的回忆和难以言说的感情。使用迅疾而猛烈的<strong>华丽暴力</strong>，将噩梦摧毁殆尽。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >醒目的色彩和富有表现力的线条营造出一种超现实的错乱和紧张感。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将不同的攻击风格搭配组合，打造无穷无尽的华丽连击。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结交使魔，利用他们的远程魔法扭转战局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过慢动作闪避、精彩格挡或吸血攻击等美德之技，打造个性化角色。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用回溯功能，立即重启一场失败的战斗，争取更满意的结果。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/896460/extras/tumblr_p0k3l33S4R1vecx2so1_640.JPG?t=1763928324\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意！该游戏包含可能会刺激光敏性癫痫患者的闪烁图案。敬请查看下方警告。</p>",
